parent1.code: a photo of a silver robot dancing in the style of cyberpunk. It twirls on the neon-lit streets in the futuristic city on a rainy night, sparks flying from its joints, with holographic advertisements floating in the air.

offspring.code: A watercolor of a sleek, iridescent silver robot gracefully dancing in the style of retro-futuristic cyberpunk. It elegantly twirls on the glistening, neon-drenched streets in the sprawling, vertical metropolis on a misty night, vibrant sparks cascading from its fluid joints, with shimmering, translucent holographic advertisements floating ethereally in the smog-filled air.
